    // Derive the logic equation from K-map
    // From the K-map:
    // cd\ab  00  01  11  10
    // 00     0   1   0   1
    // 01     1   0   1   0
    // 11     0   1   0   1
    // 10     1   0   1   0
    
    // Output is 1 when:
    // - cd=00 and ab=01 or ab=10 
